<decoDesc>
<summary>Each page contains a multichrome miniature below the written area. Legends are written in red in the upper margin.
The miniatures described here are only the first four miniatures of the manuscript.</summary>

<decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1">
<locus target="#2r"/>
<desc>God the Father holding a <term key="codex" ana="#codex">codex</term> in his left hand and <term key="gestureblessing" ana="#gestureblessing">performing blessing</term> with his right hand.
<q xml:lang="am">እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ዓለማት፡ እንደነበረ፡</q></desc>
</decoNote>

<decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2">
<locus target="#2v"/>
<desc>God creating <term key="angel" ana="#angel">angels.</term>
<q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ፈጠሮሙ፡ <add place="above">ለ</add>መላእክት፡ በዕለተ፡ እኁድ፡</q></desc>
</decoNote>

<decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3">
<locus target="#3r"/>
<desc>God flanked by archangels in the upper register, a conquered devil in the lower register.</desc>
<q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ነጻሕኮ፡ ለዲያብሎስ፡ በትዕቢቱ፡</q>
</decoNote>

<decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4">
<locus target="#3v"/>
<desc>God accompanied by the Four Heavenly Creatures in the upper register, conquered devils in the lower register.</desc>  
<q xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ አሠርኮሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡</q>
</decoNote>

</decoDesc>
                          
